    <highlightable><p>Git, though remarkably handy and powerful, is also remarkably hard to use sometimes. Though you can learn the basics easily enough, it can be really tough to dig yourself out of certain corners if you don&#8217;t understand what&#8217;s going on under the covers.</p>


	<p>This page provides links to documents, how-tos, cheat sheets, tips, and tricks related to learning and using git.</p></highlightable>
